{"tid":1467574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不分不割 要打輿論戰啦！！","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:23:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:23:55.000Z","uid":107998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"362826e872c5b2415fa7aa49a4fba434cbca06c0","tid":1467574,"uid":107998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:23:55.000Z","msg":"一直以黎，五毛、三毛入侵各個論壇，意圖分化分割香港人。<br />\n<br />\n機埸呢張好牌玩到爛咗？<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">爛你老母！</span></strong><br />\n今次香港人輸咗？<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">輸你老母！</span></strong><br />\n現埸邊個邊個係鬼？<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">鬼你老母！</span></strong><br />\n民意逆轉？<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">逆你老母！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><strong>香港人，我地大大話話有二百萬人呀！<br />\n梗係有好多唔同意見架啦！<br />\n<br />\n最重要嘅係，經過討論，做出一個適當嘅決定！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">只要<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>同<span style=\"color: orange;\">前線勇武</span>嘅意見、立埸，我地都不分化、不割席</strong></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>仲會輸乜嘢呀？</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人&hellip;我地無嘢可以輸架啦，仲驚乜嘢呀？！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">五大訴求，決一不可！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人！堅持落去！</span></span></strong>"}]}